@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam participantBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam actorBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam actorBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam boundaryBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam boundaryBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam controlBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam controlBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam entityBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam entityBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam databaseBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam databaseBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Khach hang\n(Customer)" as User #Yellow
boundary "MyRegistrationsPage\n(Next.js Frontend)" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AuthGuard" as AuthGuard #Yellow
boundary "useAuth hook" as AuthHook #Yellow
boundary "api.ts\n(Axios)" as Axios #Yellow
control "JwtMiddleware" as JWT #Yellow
control "BookingsController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "BookingService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "UnitOfWork" as UoW #Yellow
database "GenericRepository\nBooking" as Repo #Yellow
database "GenericRepository\nCustomer" as RepoC #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

== 1: Xem danh sach booking cua toi (GET /api/Bookings/my - [Authorize]) ==

User -> UI : 1: Mo trang My Bookings (/registrations/my)
activate UI

UI -> AuthGuard : 1.1: Kiem tra authentication
activate AuthGuard
alt [1.1.1] Chua dang nhap
    AuthGuard --> UI : 1.1.1.1: Redirect /login
else [1.1.2] Da dang nhap
    AuthGuard --> UI : 1.1.2.1: Render
end
deactivate AuthGuard

UI -> UI : 1.2: Render Navbar, Hero, danh sach booking

UI -> AuthHook : 1.3: useAuth() lay user
activate AuthHook
AuthHook --> UI : 1.3.1: Tra ve user (co userId)
deactivate AuthHook

UI -> UI : 1.4: useQuery(['myRegistrations', userId])
UI -> Axios : 1.5: api.get('/Bookings/my', { params: { PageSize: 50 } })
activate Axios
note right: Axios interceptor tu dong\nthem Bearer token

Axios -> JWT : 1.6: HTTP GET /api/Bookings/my?PageSize=50
activate JWT

JWT -> JWT : 1.6.1: Doc & validate JWT token
alt [1.6.2] Token hop le
    JWT -> JWT : 1.6.2.1: Verify HMAC-SHA256, issuer, audience
    JWT -> JWT : 1.6.2.2: Attach User vao HttpContext.Items
else [1.6.3] Token khong hop le
    note right: [Authorize] tra ve 401
end
JWT -> Ctrl : 1.6.4: Chuyen tiep request
deactivate JWT

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.6.5: Lay userId tu claims: ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.6.6: GetMyBookingsAsync(userId, page=1, pageSize=50)
activate Svc

Svc -> RepoC : 1.6.6.1: Customers.FirstOrDefaultAsync(c => c.UserId == userId)
activate RepoC
RepoC -> DB : 1.6.6.1.1: SELECT ... FROM Customers WHERE UserId = {userId}
activate DB
DB --> RepoC : 1.6.6.1.2: Customer hoac null
deactivate DB

alt [1.6.6.2] Khong tim thay Customer
    Svc --> Ctrl : 1.6.6.2.1: ApiResponse<PagedResult>(empty)
else [1.6.6.3] Co Customer
    deactivate RepoC

    Svc -> UoW : 1.6.6.3.1: Bookings.GetQueryable()\n.Include(Customer)\n.Include(Tour)\n.Where(b => b.CustomerId == customer.Id)
    activate UoW
    UoW -> Repo : 1.6.6.3.2: IQueryable<Booking>
    deactivate UoW

    Repo -> Repo : 1.6.6.3.3: CountAsync()
    Repo -> DB : 1.6.6.3.4: SELECT ... FROM Bookings b\nLEFT JOIN Customers c ON b.CustomerId = c.Id\nLEFT JOIN Tours t ON b.TourId = t.Id\nWHERE b.CustomerId = {customerId}\nORDER BY b.CreatedAt DESC\nOFFSET 0 LIMIT 50
    activate DB
    DB --> Repo : 1.6.6.3.5: List<Booking>
    deactivate DB

    Repo --> Svc : 1.6.6.3.6: List<Booking>
    Svc -> Svc : 1.6.6.3.7: AutoMapper.Map -> List<BookingResponse>
    Svc --> Ctrl : 1.6.6.3.8: ApiResponse<PagedResult<BookingResponse>>
end
deactivate Svc

Ctrl --> Axios : 1.6.7: HTTP 200 + JSON
deactivate Ctrl

Axios --> UI : 1.6.8: res.data.data.items
deactivate Axios

UI -> UI : 1.6.9: Map bookings -> display format
note right: Moi booking hien thi:\n- Ma booking (code)\n- Ten tour (tourName)\n- Ngay khoi hanh (startDate)\n- So khach (numAdults+numChildren)\n- Tong tien (finalPrice)\n- Trang thai (status badge)
UI --> User : 1.6.10: Hien thi danh sach booking

== 2: Xem chi tiet hoa don (Modal - Client side) ==

User -> UI : 2: Click vao ma booking de xem hoa don
activate UI

UI -> UI : 2.1: setSelectedInvoice(booking)
UI --> User : 2.2: Mo Modal "VIETTOUR RECEIPT"
note right: Modal hien thi:\n- Ma hoa don (#booking.code)\n- Ngay khoi hanh\n- Ten tour\n- So khach\n- Phi dich vu 5%\n- Tong cong (finalPrice)\n- Trang thai hien tai
deactivate UI

== 3: Xem danh sach tours (public - GET /api/Tours) ==

User -> UI : 3: Nhan "Kham Pha Tour" -> tours page
activate UI

UI -> Axios : 3.1: api.get('/Tours', { params: { Page: 1, PageSize: 50 } })
activate Axios
note right: Endpoint public - khong can token

Axios -> Ctrl : 3.2: HTTP GET /api/Tours?Page=1&PageSize=50
activate Ctrl
note right: Khong co [Authorize] -\nJwtMiddleware van chay\nnhung co the khong co user

Ctrl -> Svc : 3.3: GetAllAsync(filter)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 3.3.1: SELECT ... FROM Tours\nLEFT JOIN TourTypes\nLEFT JOIN TourImages\nWHERE IsActive=true\nORDER BY CreatedAt DESC\nOFFSET 0 LIMIT 50
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 3.3.2: List<Tour>
deactivate DB

Svc --> Ctrl : 3.3.3: ApiResponse<PagedResult<TourResponse>>
deactivate Svc

Ctrl --> Axios : 3.3.4: HTTP 200 + JSON
deactivate Ctrl

Axios --> UI : 3.3.5: res.data
deactivate Axios

UI -> UI : 3.3.6: Filter + render tour grid
UI --> User : 3.3.7: Hien thi danh sach tours
deactivate UI

@enduml
